0:

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: motivation parrot
des: This is a simple skill that gives users motivational quotes. When feeling unhappy or demotivated, users can invoke this skill and ask Alexa to 'Say a quote', or simply ask it to 'say something good' and it gives out a motivational quote by some of the most influential and widely recognized personalities.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
